### WhatsApp CRM API — request collection
### Use with the VS Code "REST Client" extension, or adapt to curl/Postman.
### 1) run `npm run seed`  2) run `npm run dev`  3) login below to get @token

@host = http://localhost:4000
@token = PASTE_TOKEN_FROM_LOGIN

### Health
GET {{host}}/health

### Login (Administrator)
# @name login
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "priya@greenwood.edu", "password": "password123" }

### Who am I (paste token above first)
GET {{host}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── Leads ──
GET {{host}}/api/leads?page=1&perPage=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Leads filtered by owner + search
GET {{host}}/api/leads?owner=Priya Kothari&q=aanya
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Convert a reply/contact into a lead
POST {{host}}/api/leads/convert
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Test Parent", "phone": "+91 90000 11111", "source": "Inbound", "owner": "Ananya Saxena" }

### Change a lead's status (triggers follow-up rule) — replace :id
POST {{host}}/api/leads/LEAD_ID/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "statusId": "STATUS_ID" }

### Add a note
POST {{host}}/api/leads/LEAD_ID/notes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "text": "Called — interested, sending brochure" }

### ── Follow-ups ──
GET {{host}}/api/followups/buckets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Complete a follow-up
POST {{host}}/api/followups/FOLLOWUP_ID/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "outcome": "Reached, positive" }

### ── Masters / Setup ──
GET {{host}}/api/masters/statuses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create a lead status
POST {{host}}/api/masters/statuses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Application Received", "color": "#16a34a", "followUpRequired": true, "order": 8 }

### ── Users & roles ──
GET {{host}}/api/usertypes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create a user
POST {{host}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "New Counsellor", "email": "new@greenwood.edu", "passwordHash": "TEMP", "userType": "USERTYPE_ID", "status": "Active" }

### ── Campaigns ──
GET {{host}}/api/campaigns
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create a campaign
POST {{host}}/api/campaigns
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "December Fee Reminder", "template": "fee_due_reminder_v3", "category": "Fee" }

### Launch it (sends via simulation; populates message log + funnel)
POST {{host}}/api/campaigns/CAMPAIGN_ID/launch
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── Conversations (1:1, WABA) ──
GET {{host}}/api/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Reply with free text (only works if 24h window open)
POST {{host}}/api/conversations/CONV_ID/reply
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "text": "You can visit any weekday 10AM–4PM." }

### Reply with a template (works even if window closed)
POST {{host}}/api/conversations/CONV_ID/reply
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "template": "campus_visit_invite" }

### ── Message history ──
GET {{host}}/api/messages?direction=inbound
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Convert an inbound message to a lead
POST {{host}}/api/messages/MESSAGE_ID/convert
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── Conversion analytics ──
GET {{host}}/api/conversion/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── WhatsApp vendor accounts (multi-vendor, one active) ──
GET {{host}}/api/whatsapp-accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Add a Pinnacle account (fill real values from their doc)
POST {{host}}/api/whatsapp-accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "Pinnacle – Admissions",
  "vendor": "pinnacle",
  "senderNumber": "+91 99999 12345",
  "apiBaseUrl": "https://api.pinnacle.example",
  "apiKey": "YOUR_PINNACLE_KEY",
  "verifyToken": "pinnacle-verify"
}

### Add a Meta-direct account
POST {{host}}/api/whatsapp-accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "Meta Direct – Main",
  "vendor": "meta",
  "phoneNumberId": "YOUR_PHONE_NUMBER_ID",
  "accessToken": "YOUR_META_TOKEN",
  "appSecret": "YOUR_APP_SECRET",
  "verifyToken": "greenwood-verify"
}

### Activate one account (deactivates the rest)
POST {{host}}/api/whatsapp-accounts/ACCOUNT_ID/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Which vendor is currently active?
GET {{host}}/api/system/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── WhatsApp webhook (vendor → us; per-tenant URL) ──
GET {{host}}/webhooks/whatsapp/TENANT_ID?hub.mode=subscribe&hub.verify_token=greenwood-verify&hub.challenge=12345

